<section class="ks-shipping">
  <div class="ks-shipping-inner">

    <div class="ks-shipping-hero">
      <p class="ks-shipping-overline">✝ Kingdom Supply</p>
      <h1 class="ks-shipping-title">Shipping & Returns</h1>
      <p class="ks-shipping-subtitle">Every order is handled with care and shipped with purpose.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ks-shipping-blocks">

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">📦</div>
        <h2>Order Processing</h2>
        <p>All orders are processed within 24–72 hours of being placed. You will receive a confirmation email with tracking information once your order has shipped.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">🌍</div>
        <h2>Shipping Times</h2>
        <p>We ship worldwide. Estimated delivery times are 7–12 business days for the USA, Canada, and international destinations. Delays may occur during peak seasons.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">🚚</div>
        <h2>Free Shipping</h2>
        <p>Free worldwide shipping on all orders over $50. Orders under $50 are subject to a standard shipping fee calculated at checkout based on your location.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">↩️</div>
        <h2>Returns & Exchanges</h2>
        <p>We offer hassle-free returns and exchanges within 14 days of delivery. Items must be unused and in original condition. Sale items are final sale.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">⚡</div>
        <h2>Damaged or Wrong Item</h2>
        <p>If you received a damaged or incorrect item, email us within 7 days of delivery and we will make it right — no questions asked.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ks-shipping-block">
        <div class="ks-shipping-icon">✉️</div>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any shipping or return inquiries, reach us at <strong>support@kingdomsupply.com</strong>. We respond within 24 hours, Monday through Friday.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="ks-shipping-closing">
      <p>"Whatever you do, work at it with all your heart, as working for the Lord."</p>
      <span>— Colossians 3:23</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.ks-shipping {
  background: #0A0A0A;
  padding: 80px 40px;
  color: #FAFAF5;
}
.ks-shipping-inner {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.ks-shipping-hero {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
}
.ks-shipping-overline {
  font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #C9A84C;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.ks-shipping-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 52px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: #FAFAF5;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.ks-shipping-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #CCCCCC;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.ks-shipping-blocks {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 40px;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
}
.ks-shipping-block {
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  padding: 40px;
}
.ks-shipping-icon {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.ks-shipping-block h2 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: #C9A84C;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.ks-shipping-block p {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  color: #CCCCCC;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.ks-shipping-block strong {
  color: #C9A84C;
}
.ks-shipping-closing {
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  padding-top: 60px;
}
.ks-shipping-closing p {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 24px;
  color: #FAFAF5;
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto 16px;
}
.ks-shipping-closing span {
  font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #C9A84C;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .ks-shipping { padding: 60px 20px; }
  .ks-shipping-title { font-size: 32px; }
  .ks-shipping-subtitle { font-size: 17px; }
  .ks-shipping-blocks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .ks-shipping-block { padding: 28px; }
  .ks-shipping-closing p { font-size: 18px; }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "KS Shipping",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "KS Shipping" }]
}
{% endschema %}
